Date - format is (m)mddyy: T - mean daily temperature in celcius
PanE - Pan Evaporation (the predictand) in cm/day
You should use the five predictors (T,W,SR,DSP,DRH) or a subset or combination of these to model PanE
The data represent daily environmental factors at a site in San Diego, USA; 1/1/1987 - 31/12/1990
